prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist greeting card front cover, flat 2D illustration. The scene is a humorous and charming beach setting with a clean, off-white background.

In the center, an illustrated cartoon version of Lao Lao from the photo is struggling comically to build a lopsided, slightly-too-large sandcastle. She has a look of focused determination mixed with a bit of funny frustration. She is wearing the light blue sweatshirt (logo removed) and black pants from the photo.

Next to her, the cartoon version of Jordan from the photo, wearing his brown hoodie and dark pants, is playfully "helping" by very seriously and carefully placing a single, tiny seashell on top of the leaning sandcastle tower with tweezers, as if it's the most critical architectural element. He has a slight, knowing smirk.

Around them on the "sand" (a simple beige shape at the bottom third of the card) are minimalist beach elements: a couple of simple starfish and a misplaced beach pail. The overall feeling is clean, light, and funny.

Centered above the illustration, in a beautiful, readable, elegant black handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao".
